{
  "stem": "6719.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, you know, like I said, that gave us-- ugh, gave us-- we had access because-- because of the nature of the beast.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You went everywhere, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every camp, you know, there were sections, A, B, C, D, E.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was a women camp, so we-- wherever there was a job required, that's where we went.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, that's something that's inbred.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, when-- where I come from-- if I may use that term-- women were put on a pedestal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, you didn't speak badly to women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe some people did, but not where I-- where I was, OK?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Women were something special.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Uh, women didn't work, although they worked their-- their-- their heads off at home, but I say the term of worked in an office, or something like that, although some did.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I saw how women were treated by women, mind you not, SS wome-- SS men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "SS women and kapo women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know-- OK, I'll give you a really-- a quickie down there that-- that-- that signifies what I'm saying.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I forgot about that-- that-- I had a job very briefly for about four or five days that, uh-- that, uh, picked up kettles of soup.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was in the very beginning, [INAUDIBLE], after the [INAUDIBLE], after the tailor shop, whatever, in between somewhere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can't get it straight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, and we delivered soup to a-- a-- kommandos, in other words, the work details that worked outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, uh, one day we, uh-- we-- it was in a truck, a motorized truck, a camion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we drove up with these kettles to deliver the soup at lunch time.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
